SnS2-coop-cohp
COOP
Sn-S        : name of the curve
Sn          : first orbital kind (here: all on Sn)
2.0 4.0     : distance range in Ang (to catch just nearest neighbors)
S           : second orbital kind
Sn4dxy-S3s  : another curve
Sn_4dxy     : only 4dxy orbitals
2.0 4.0
S_3s        : only 3s orbitals on the second atom
